column5: Team Three is in the lead with 201"  That is all.  Gerritt.
SSSSSSSSSSHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHH Not so loud,team five might hear ya and have to catch another fish to SHUT YA UP.LOL  Morning bud.
Yeah yeah yeah....team 6 is in third....but the first and second place teams have 2 more fish than we do.  Once we get on the board with those, you'll be looking up at us!!! LOL  Morning Gerritt!!!

Well its about time.  The Up Scalers have been fishing off the Party Boat for a while all by ourselves thinking that so one is interested in this little friendly compition. Now if we can get the rest off them going it will be alot more fun congrats on the lead.    l want a recount LOL.  Let the game begin.   Peace  Ken   PS   FISH ON lol
Ya so team 4 is in 5th The Hare and the turtle haven't finished the race and now you just jinxed your team Gerritt  It aint over till its over.MTP

Ya gotta love the gloating.   Enjoy it while it lasts.     Pretty soon you'll all be looking up at Team 9 Anglers Anonymous.  I'll be fishing the french in about 2 weeks and have a 50" ski, a 30" cat, a 40" pike, a 20" Bass and a 30" eye with my name on it.  I figure 327" should be enough to finish in 1st.  FOTB

I noticed that one inch and was just waiting on you to mention it.  Dang, this just means Up Scalers will have to replace the fish we already have.  Congrats on the great fishing guys...  This is way too much fun!!  Cheers  Jen
lol.. i noticed the 1inch since shawn got those nice fish.. GO TEAM 3!!
